request.description:
Customer Registeration Endpoint
Create a new customer
{
    "profile": {
        "email": "segbukenshi@yahoo.com"| Email address of customer,
        "password": "password"| Password of customer,
        "full_name": "Segun Okunuga"| Full name of customer,
        "is_individual": ""| Customer Type | 0 - SME , 1 - Individual,
        "phone": "07034400026"| Phone Number of Customer
    }
}

Create a savings plan
Create a new savings plan for a customer
{
    "plan": {
        "title": "Car Purchase"|Title of the plan,
        "amount": "10"|Amount to be saved ,
        "target": "100"|Target for a plan if any,
        "frequency": "2"|Frequency of the savings plan|1 - Daily , 2 - Monthly , 4 - Weekly,
        "duration": "12"|How long the plan is going to run,
        "start_date": "2020-10-31"|The date the plan is to start,
        "funding_source": "1"|Source of the funds for the plan |1 - Cards 2 - Cash Transfer| Default is 1 which is cards,
        "category":"1"|The category of the savings|Not required,
        "automated":"1"|Is the savings automated|Not required
    },
    "card": {
        "connected_card_id": "86640"|The card to be used to fund the period savings|Unique ID from list of customer cards
    },
    "token": ""|Customer Login Token
}

Savings Quick save 
Save a certain amount in a savings plan
{
    "token":""|Customer login token,
    "payload":{
        "plan_id":""|Unique ID for savings request,
        "reference":""|Reference of the transaction from paystack,
        "amount":""|Amount to be saved
    }

}

Savings Withdrawal
Withdraw from a customer savings
{
    "token":""|Customer token,
    "payload":{
        "plan_id":"1234"|Unique id from the savings,
        "amount":"100000"|Amount to withdraw,
        "account_selected":"12"|Customer bank account to transfer the funds to| The unique id from list of customer bank accounts
    }
}

Create Investment
Create a new investment for a customer
{
    "plan": {
        "duration": "1"|The duration for the investment in months,
        "amount": "10"|The amount the customer wants to invest,
        "product_id": "2823"|The product the customer is investing in
    },
    "token": ""|Customer login token,
    "paystack": {
        "reference": ""|Reference for the paystack transaction if a customer uses card to fund the transaction
    }
}
NB: Paystack object to be left out if customer did not fund the investment using a card

Investment Rollover
Rollover a customer investment
{
    "token":""|Customer login token,
    "payload":{
        "plan_id":"1234"|Investment id from the investment record,
        "duration":"1"|Duration for the rollover in months
    }

}

Investment Top Up
Top Up a customer investment
{
    "token":""|Customer login token,
    "payload":{
        "plan_id":"1234"|Investment id from the investment record,
        "amount":"10000"|Amount for top up
    },
    "paystack":{
        "reference":"123456"|Reference for the paystack transaction if a customer uses card to fund the transaction
    }
}
NB: Paystack object to be left out if customer did not fund the investment using a card

Investment Liquidate
Liquidate a customer investment - Withdraw part of an active investment
{
    "token":""|Customer token,
    "payload":{
        "plan_id":"1234"|Investment id of the investment to liquidate from,
        "amount":"100000"|Amount to liquidate,
        "withdrawal_bank_id":"12"|Customer bank account to transfer the funds to| The unique id from list of customer bank accounts
    }
}

Investment Terminate
Terminate a customer investment - Close an active investment
{
    "token":""|Customer token,
    "payload":{
        "plan_id":"1234"|Investment id of the investment to liquidate from
        "withdrawal_bank_id":"12"|Customer bank account to transfer the funds to| The unique id from list of customer bank accounts
    }
}

